title: 02/15/2021 - Hour 3 - Jordan Palmer, LA's Top 10 Athletes
itunes:title: 02/15/2021 - Hour 3 - Jordan Palmer, LA's Top 10 Athletes
description:
In this hour of The Herd with Colin Cowherd, former NFL quarterback Jordan Palmer stops by The Herd to talk about the NFL's young quarterbacks and the next possible home for Philadelphia's Carson Wentz. Plus, Colin's Top 10 Athletes in Los Angeles.
